
Modifiers/Access Specifiers:
----------------------------
Class Level
default:
We can access only with in same package
1)By creating 	object in sane class
2)Same package sub class 
3)Same package by creating object in other class

Outside the package it is not allowed.

public

Inside and Oustide the package we can access either by creating objects or through inheritance


1)

Member level modifeirs
----------------------
private
protected

Illegal modifier for the class A; only public, abstract & final are permitted

